data.description: Explore this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the gated Villa Sol community. Newly upgraded kitchen and bathrooms feature Quartz countertops and new cabinets. Enjoy the benefits of paid-off solar panels, fresh new laminate flooring and New A/C just insalled. Villa Sol offers a clubhouse, gym, outdoor pool, tennis, and basketball courts. Low Hoa covers Internet, Cable and Ground Maint. Plus, you're just minutes away from major theme parks. Don't miss this opportunity – contact us today for a viewing!
